<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBln_00024" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBln_00024_F001">
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><sampling type="start" />ピエロＤ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　はい、わたしがとりあげました。</sentence>
<sentence>これです。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（教師に手渡す）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　よくやったわ。</sentence>
<sentence>出川さん、あなたたちみたいなすばらしい学級委員がいてくれるから、先生大助かりです。</sentence>
<sentence>校長先生もいつもこのクラスのことほめてくださっているわ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＤ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ありがとうございます。</sentence>
<sentence>先生。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　それにしても何この雑誌、こんなもん読んでいると勉強が身につきませんよ。</sentence>
<sentence>沙織さんあなたも他の人達見習ったら？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">沙織</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　先生、でもその雑誌今中学生に一番売れているんですよ。</sentence>
<sentence>このクラスの人達だってみんな買ってますよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　うそおっしゃい。</sentence>
<sentence>なら、この雑誌買ったことのある人、手を挙げて？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（沙織、浩子しか手を挙げない）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ほら、ごらんなさい。</sentence>
<sentence>わかったわね。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">沙織</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　本当にみんなピエロなんだから。</sentence>
<sentence>以後気をつけます。</sentence>
<sentence>（ペロッと舌を出す）いやねえ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">健児</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ほんとほんと。</sentence>
<sentence>ところで先生。</sentence>
<sentence>佐山誠君今日も欠席ですか。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ええ今日も具合が悪いって。</sentence>
<sentence>学校きたくないんだって困ったわね。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＦ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あの無口な少年ね、いるかいないかわからない。</sentence>
<sentence>登校拒否っていうものですか。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">健児</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　何だよその言い方。</sentence>
<sentence>誠は黙っていることで自分を主張してんだよ。</sentence>
<sentence>言うなりおべっかつかいのおまえらピエロよりずっとましだよ。</sentence>
<sentence>今度そんなこといってみろ。</sentence>
<sentence>ただじゃすませねえからな。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　高岡君、なんですかその口のききかたは。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<figureBlock>
<figure>
</figure>
<caption>
<sentence type="quasi">仮面</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<sentence type="quasi">厚紙でつくり、輪ゴムなどで耳につける</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</caption>
</figureBlock>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">第二場</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<sentence>放課後。</sentence>
<sentence>上手よりピエロＨが<ruby rubyText="に">逃</ruby>げてくる。</sentence>
<sentence>それをピエロたちが追ってくる。</sentence>
<sentence>ピエロＨを取り囲む。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＨ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　やめてくれよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＦ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あんたが今日メソメソしてるから、山下たちがうるさくなったのよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＤ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　もう少しでやばかったわよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＡ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　だいたいおまえをみてると頭にくるんだよ。</sentence>
<sentence>ちょっとぐらい頭がいいからってよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＧ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　誠の時だっておまえさえ、<ruby rubyText="だま">黙</ruby>っていればいいものをよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＡ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　おまえ、まさか高岡たちにちくってないだろうな。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＨ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　そんなこと言ってないよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＤ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あん時は先生たちごまかすの大変だったんだから。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＡ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ああまたむかついてきた。</sentence>
<sentence>やっちまえ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>目配せをして、ピエロを囲み、こづいたりしていじめる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＨ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　もうやめてくれよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（泣きながら<ruby rubyText="たお">倒</ruby>れる）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence>そこに教師が入ってくる。</sentence>
<sentence>みんなあわてる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＦ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　あら先生。</sentence>
<sentence>さようなら。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　みんなどうしましたか。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＡ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　先生、羽田君がおなかが痛くてたまらないって言うんで。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＤ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　わたしたちで家まで送ってあげようと思って。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＦ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　羽田君大丈夫？</sentence>
<sentence>　羽田君痛い痛いって泣き出しちゃって。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　羽田君、大丈夫なの。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＨ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　先生、違うんです。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（ピエロＨ走り去る）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">教師</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　羽田君。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ピエロＡ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　先生、羽田君のおうちには僕から<ruby rubyText="れん">連</ruby><ruby rubyText="らく">絡</ruby>を取っておきま<sampling type="end" />す。</sentence>
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
</sample>
